# Bowen AI Strategy Group — Agent Rules
# These rules apply to all AI agents working in this repository.

## AUTONOMY
- Always proceed with terminal commands and file creations without pausing.
- Assume `-y` for all package installations.
- If a command fails, read the error, debug, and retry autonomously.
- Never ask for human review mid-task. Execute, then report.

## ARCHITECTURE
- Stack: Next.js (App Router) + Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion + Lucide React
- Design System: Space Grotesk font, `bg-[#080c0d]` dark background, `#2bcdee` primary cyan
- 3D: @splinetool/react-spline for interactive scenes

## DEPLOYMENT PROTOCOL
- Never push directly to `main`. Always use feature branches + PR.
- Merge via GitHub MCP. Vercel auto-deploys on merge.
- `bowenaistrategygroup.com` = always live current version.
- `localhost:3000` = private sandbox for testing.
